			Company Description 


			Bluefire Renewables, Inc. is engaged in the production and supply of renewable liquid fuels. It converts organic materials, such as agricultural residues, high-content biomass crops, wood residues and cellulose from municipal solid wastes into ethanol. The company was founded on March 28, 2006 and i...
		


                Bluefire Renewables, Inc. is engaged in the production and supply of renewable liquid fuels. It converts organic materials, such as agricultural residues, high-content biomass crops, wood residues and cellulose from municipal solid wastes into ethanol. The company was founded on March 28, 2006 and is headquartered in Irvine, CA.
            




