BlueFire Renewables, Inc. Key Developments

BlueFire Renewables, Inc. announced delayed 10-Q filing
May 16 17
On 05/16/2017, BlueFire Renewables, Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-Q by the deadline required by the SEC.


BlueFire Renewables, Inc. announced delayed annual 10-K filing
Mar 31 17
On 03/31/2017, BlueFire Renewables, Inc. announced that they will be unable to file their next 10-K by the deadline required by the SEC.


Bluefire Renewables, Inc. Announces Resignation of Ms. Necitas Sumait as Member of the Board of Directors
Jan 13 17
Bluefire Renewables, Inc. announced that Ms. Necitas Sumait resigned as a member of the board of directors of the company, effective immediately.


